subs.text: Another great Peloton song -- We Didn't Start The Fire by Billy Joel.

If you liked Severance but have only seen it once, watch it again. I found there were a lot of things that only made sense when you'd seen it all the way through. And I missed a bunch of stuff the first time around.
Twitter could use the smarts of my Tesla Model 3. It could let me do moderation for myself the same way I tell my car how I want it to drive.
